    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the fable of discovery and diversity…</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/5f8f1bc016b1ceb4fa00efbaf9071416.poster.avif?t=1762862341\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/5f8f1bc016b1ceb4fa00efbaf9071416.webm?t=1762862341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/5f8f1bc016b1ceb4fa00efbaf9071416.mp4?t=1762862341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the dreams of animals, from moments of peace to thrilling adventures. Let's explore the places where only traces of human presence linger. The decision of your destination is entirely up to you. Become a deer and run through a starry world of dreaming, where the past and imagination are blended. Meet different animals and peek into their strange dreams.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/3cc1b0c56e59e0bfd2fa0563100ce802.poster.avif?t=1762862341\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/3cc1b0c56e59e0bfd2fa0563100ce802.webm?t=1762862341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033560/extras/3cc1b0c56e59e0bfd2fa0563100ce802.mp4?t=1762862341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe this third-person adventure game will become your recent dream, too!</p>",
